snippet.title: Radiangames JoyJoy - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Radiangames JoyJoy is now available on Xbox Live Indie Games.  JoyJoy is the first game in the Radiangames series of small, high-quality games for Xbox Live Indie Games.  

An alpha build of JoyJoy was the #1 US-ranked game in the 2010 Dream.Build.Play competition (#6 overall).
